{"tid":1427622,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入！依家PoPo會換上黑色衫，混入示威者入面放流料","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:21:14.000Z","uid":5918,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"66a306de576960be48c48b18e1e6ab48b231b21d","tid":1427622,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"混入黎最主要唔係扮衝擊，係會喺人群當中散布有狗車黎緊或者將會被包圍言論想嘛走你地<br />\n<br />\n利申：前日發夢喺沙田撚左大半日狗都無隻，喺狗屋出面有條友無啦啦出黎邊行邊叫話源禾路出黑旗，手足即刻退後左，Fact check左之後先發現流料。<br />\n<br />\n隔左兩個鐘，我認撚得同一個人又走出黎話有狗車喺大圍出緊黎，我即刻大叫咪撚信，Fact check左先，當然又係流料。<br />\n<br />\n所以下次有可疑人士Fact Check都未有就放風既，咪撚俾佢走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d287781cbfd8134d04668c2405f8fbf7cec11d4","tid":1427622,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ef694ccd1244ce3af4a2c93f1c0b1214b08367d","tid":1427622,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:03:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f923fe95a754f29122cac4199eb9d830c97e84a6","tid":1427622,"uid":181778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ee00ce4199c1442079b05a77d4596d6f017c542","tid":1427622,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"據上次所見，對方會係單拖友，邊行邊大叫放風，無人識佢，下次識做"},{"pid":"1fb963290636049cb302630048f9bcc50004db0b","tid":1427622,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"286fbe73b02faf7f80f2e9529f430eeec20dfdda","tid":1427622,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba9ff63eba8a8872475befc8fee824892bbbe608","tid":1427622,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"